metadata.name: Achromatic Symphony
metadata.description: Chromosome Symphony is a stunning exploration of the intricate structure and symbolism of DNA. Against a black background, rainbowcore colors in light teal and light crimson swirl and dance to create mysterious forms reminiscent of the cosmic wonders of the universe. The varied textures and poster art style add to the sense of artistic experimentation and expression. Is a powerful and enigmatic portrait of the building blocks of life.
